snippet.title: On Thin Ice
snippet.description:
BONUS VIDEO!!!!

PLEASE SIGN YANKEE WALLY GET HER REASSIGNED!!!!! Copy and paste the link below xxxxx


https://www.change.org/p/twitter-inc-bring-yankee-wally-back-to-twitter?original_footer_petition_id=22926735&algorithm=promoted&source_location=petition_footer&grid_position=10&pt=AVBldGl0aW9uAIJ3wwEAAAAAYNf5Dbh8kTQ4Y2Q5NjM5ZA%3D%3D

I think Meghan and Harry's personal Royal Expert is skating on thin ice!! Omid has managed to shut down Yankee Wally's account! and for what?? Free Speech? The right to be able to have an opinion?? Pretty ironic from the man that has recently launched an attack on Prince William's staff and accused them of plating false stories!! Show us the evidence?????

The fact ITV received phone call from Kensington Palace saying if you go ahead this IS defamatory... well that says everything! The palace are indeed fighting back and Omid has picked a side long ago. I hope it serves him well x
